{
  "texts": [
    "The validation and testing sets consist of 50 images each, and each set contains images of varying resolutions.",
    "In the testing set, the resolution of images is not fixed, ranging from 1280 × 720 to 5760 × 5760.",
    "Note that the ground truth data corresponding to the validation and testing dataset is not publicly available.",
    "Data augmentation.",
    "Due to our inability to accurately model defective pixels, inspired by [28], we extract the defect pixels map from the training data of the challenge to generate more diverse and realistic inputs."
  ]
}